Jay Dyer is a public speaker, lecturer, comedian and author of Esoteric Hollywood: Sex, Cults and Symbols in Film, as well as the host of the JaysAnalysis Podcast/Esoteric Hollywood.
He is also a regular contributor to 21stCenturyWire, Soul of the East and the Espionage History Archive. Jay’s work covers a wide variety of subjects, including metaphysics, film analysis, theology, geopolitics, literature, and history. Jay returns to Red Ice to discuss the recent mass shooting that took place in Las Vegas.
We discuss the various odd circumstances regarding the event, ranging from the high kill ratio to Stephen Paddock’s curious background. Jay reminds us that the mainstream media isn’t to be trusted, given their slanted coverage of mass shootings in the past.
